00:02:25.400 --> 00:02:28.310
- Okay, question: how do you
know when to move up in bands?

00:02:28.310 --> 00:02:30.210
Is there a certain number to hit?

00:02:30.210 --> 00:02:32.930
Yes, because we're using
variable resistance

00:02:32.930 --> 00:02:34.560
this is an X3 specific question.

00:02:34.560 --> 00:02:38.590
I also wanna know that this
series is not just gonna be

00:02:38.590 --> 00:02:40.990
about X3, it's gonna be
falsehoods of fitness

00:02:40.990 --> 00:02:43.630
as in applied to all types of fitness,

00:02:43.630 --> 00:02:45.330
so this will be shareable
to anybody you know

00:02:45.330 --> 00:02:46.850
